    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871010/extras/6e656411445c318d04898f9f6185c464.poster.avif?t=1647669344\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871010/extras/6e656411445c318d04898f9f6185c464.webm?t=1647669344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871010/extras/6e656411445c318d04898f9f6185c464.mp4?t=1647669344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏概述</h2>标题：'Dubu Rush'<br>类型：冒险<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>一个按钮操作方法</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>可爱的圆点字符</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>击败和有趣的音乐</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871010/extras/9a610254f5e5e6175ff197c3ef1e75ef.poster.avif?t=1647669344\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871010/extras/9a610254f5e5e6175ff197c3ef1e75ef.webm?t=1647669344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871010/extras/9a610254f5e5e6175ff197c3ef1e75ef.mp4?t=1647669344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏故事</h2>   勇士们对抗国王拯救这个世界。然而，国王太高，因为它非常高。所以你需要帮助你到达这个英雄国王。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >如何取胜</h2>   要清除游戏，请使用跳转按钮增加龙。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏阶段</h2>   这场比赛的阶段由五层组成。每层都包括每个主题的设计和难度。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >混乱系统</h2>   为了调整游戏的难度，存在一个隐藏的阶段，球员遭到播放器的数量由玩家上传的播放器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >保存功能</h2>ㅤ玩家的位置和时间自动保存。当它被清除时，播放器的晴朗时间在高分中注册。因此，玩家需要快速上升以获得高分。",
